Again, they are stiled Watchmen, so Isai. 62. v. 6. I have set Watchmen upon thy Walls, O Jerusalem [pro muris tuis pro salute tua precatores constitui Sacerdotes & Levitas] (so Grotius
               Tom. 1. Edit. Ʋlt. p. 335.
               ) And Ezek. 3. v. 17. I have made thee a Watchman to the House of Israel: To which accords that of Heb. 13. v. 17. Where the Duty of Obedience to 'em is urged on this Account. For, says the Apostle, They Watch for your Souls as they that must give an Account.
